    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Sacrifice is a <strong>turn-based puzzle game</strong> set in 17th century Salem, where <strong>you control two characters simultaneously</strong>, Sarah and the Gatekeeper. Play through <strong>30 of the 120 levels of the full game</strong> filled with clever and unique puzzles, and break the seal that keeps your lost daughter trapped.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ignite the fire!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gates of Salem are waiting. Only those who are wise enough will be able to cross them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124880/extras/4f51b87513ee76510300fc1b8ba19399.poster.avif?t=1757167418\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124880/extras/4f51b87513ee76510300fc1b8ba19399.webm?t=1757167418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124880/extras/4f51b87513ee76510300fc1b8ba19399.mp4?t=1757167418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A unique take on the genre!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your goal is to guide the gatekeeper to the golden rune. You only have a couple of turns to do that so plan ahead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124880/extras/47878e1ac10142e260d8bed2d81a2006.poster.avif?t=1757167418\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124880/extras/47878e1ac10142e260d8bed2d81a2006.webm?t=1757167418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124880/extras/47878e1ac10142e260d8bed2d81a2006.mp4?t=1757167418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Escape Death!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Death looms at every turn. Stay one step ahead of danger as you guide Sarah and the gatekeeper through treacherous puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124880/extras/014600c42538b66ff4d19a0ffa4a7b54.poster.avif?t=1757167418\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124880/extras/014600c42538b66ff4d19a0ffa4a7b54.webm?t=1757167418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124880/extras/014600c42538b66ff4d19a0ffa4a7b54.mp4?t=1757167418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Outsmart the game!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Sacrifice is all about unique puzzles and unique mechanics. With over 120 levels in the full game, you will have to think twice and strategize your moves carefully.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124880/extras/5389d01deda3d201b909c40c432d9786.poster.avif?t=1757167418\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124880/extras/5389d01deda3d201b909c40c432d9786.webm?t=1757167418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124880/extras/5389d01deda3d201b909c40c432d9786.mp4?t=1757167418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This prologue contains 30 of the +120 levels of the full game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize all kinds of cool mechanics like crazy teleporters, magical bridges and more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your actions will affect the story, what ending will you get?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secrets?</p></li></ul>",
